The European Federation for Welding, Joining and Cutting, as 30 European members and manages a harmonized international system for training qualification and certification of welding personnel. Mutually recognized in more than 40 countries worldwide.&#xd;
It is also responsible for the Certification System of companies using welding in Quality, Environment, Health and Safety.&#xd;
Considering the organizations implementing the EWF education, training qualification and certification systems for personnel and companies in the welding sector the EWF network comprises more than 1.000 organizations.
